NK041(di)035:1: // gsar rnying spyir 'gro ba'i dbang bshad bye brag so
NK041(di)035:2: so la 'khyog mtshams kyi dper brjod dang bcas pa
NK041(di)035:3: bzhugs so // swa sti sid+d+hi rastu /
NK041(di)035:4: rab 'byams dkyil 'khor 'khor lo'i dbang phyug dang //
NK041(di)035:5: tha dad ma dmigs rje btsun gter bdag gling //
NK041(di)035:6: gang gi zhabs pad spyi bor rtag mchod nas //
NK041(di)035:7: 'chad 'dod gsar bu'i dga' ston de ring spel //
NK041(di)035:9: bye brag nyer mkho kha bsgyur tshul gyi dper brjod
NK041(di)035:10: dang bcas pa cung zad cig gleng bar bya ste
NK041(di)035:11: / de yang slob ma khrus dang phyag sogs sngon du 'gro bas /
NK041(di)035:13: gleng ba skabs su bab pa dang gsal dag snyan pa'i ngag gis 'di skad ces /
NK041(di)035:14: 'o nam mkha' dang mnyam pa'i sems can thams cad
NK041(di)035:15: bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs
NK041(di)035:16: rgyas kyi go 'phang la 'god par bya /
NK041(di)035:17: de'i ched du rjes gnang ngam /
NK041(di)035:18: rdo rje theg pa'i lam gyi rtsa ba mngon par
NK041(di)035:19: dbang bskur ba zab mo gsan nas tshul bzhin du
NK041(di)035:20: nyams su blang bar bagyi'o snyam pa byang chub mchog
NK041(di)035:22: chos gsan pa'i kun tu spyod pa yang /
NK041(di)035:24: rab tu dma' ba'i stan la 'dug /
NK041(di)035:25: dul ba'i dpal ni rab tu bskyed //
NK041(di)035:26: dga' dang ldan pa'i mig gis blta //
NK041(di)035:27: tshig ni bdud rtsi 'thung ba bzhin //
NK041(di)035:30: rtog pa thams cad legs par bsdus nas ni //
NK041(di)035:31: shin tu bsam pa bzang po ldan pas nyon //
NK041(di)035:32: brjed ngas blo la rdo rje sems dpa' sogs //
NK041(di)035:33: bde bar gshegs pa rnams kyis byin mi brlab //
NK041(di)035:35: dge ba'i bshes gnyen la gus pa dang ldan pas
NK041(di)035:36: sgo gsum legs par bsdam te gzhan du ma yengs
NK041(di)035:37: pa'i sgo nas gsan par zhu 'tshal /
NK041(di)035:38: de yang 'o skol gyi ston pa yang dag par
NK041(di)035:39: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas thabs mkhas la thugs rje chen
NK041(di)035:40: po mnga' ba de nyid kyis /
NK041(di)035:41: sems can rnams kyi bsam pa dang /
NK041(di)035:43: skal pa'i khyad par dang rjes su mthun pa'i chos
NK041(di)035:44: kyi bdud rtsi bsam gyis mi khyab pa zhig bstan
NK041(di)035:45: pa thams cad kyang bsdu na /
NK041(di)035:48: sangs rgyas pa la bzhi pa dang //
NK041(di)035:49: lnga pa thub pa'i dgongs pa min //
NK041(di)035:54: theg pa gsum du rnam grol gyi theg pa thams
NK041(di)035:55: cad 'dus pas theg pa bzhi pa med mod kyang
NK041(di)035:56: / gsum po'i nang sems kyi dbye ba la brten
NK041(di)035:57: pa'i theg pa'i rnam grangs ni mang du 'byung bas
NK041(di)035:58: / mi 'gal te / lang kar gshegs pa las /
NK041(di)035:59: theg pa rnam pa mang bshad pa //
NK041(di)035:60: sems can rnams ni drang ba'i phyir //
NK041(di)035:61: theg pa tha dad ngas bshad de //
NK041(di)035:62: theg pa gcig tu ngas bstan to //
NK041(di)035:63: ji srid sems ni 'jug pa'i bar //
NK041(di)035:64: theg pa dag la thug pa med //
NK041(di)035:66: des na spyir mngon mtho'i theg pa gnyis /
NK041(di)035:67: nges par legs pa'i theg pa gsum dang lngar mdo sde las gsungs te /
NK041(di)035:69: lha yi theg dang tshangs pa'i theg /
NK041(di)035:70: de bzhin du ni nyan thos dang //
NK041(di)035:71: de bzhin gshegs dang rang rgyal gyi //
NK041(di)035:72: theg pa mtha' dag pa bshad do //
NK041(di)035:75: mngon mtho'i theg pa gnyis gcig tu bsdus /
NK041(di)035:76: nges legs kyi de bzhin gshegs pa'i theg pa la
NK041(di)035:77: byang sems dang sngags gnyis su phyes nas lngar bshad
NK041(di)035:78: pa'ang yod de / gsang snying las /
NK041(di)035:79: theg pa bzhi yis nges 'byung la //
NK041(di)035:80: theg pa gcig gi 'bras bur gnas //
NK041(di)035:82: de la mngon mtho'i theg pa ni /
NK041(di)035:83: las 'bras la yid ches pa'i sgo nas dge mi
NK041(di)035:84: dge blang dor ma nor bar spyad pas mi dang
NK041(di)035:85: 'dod lha'i go 'phang thob nus pa de'i phyir /
NK041(di)035:87: lha'i theg pa zhes gsungs pa dang /
NK041(di)035:88: de'i steng du 'jig rten pa'i bsam gtan dang gzugs med kyi ting nge 'dzin bsgom pa ni /
NK041(di)035:89: 'dod nyon gyis gtsang bas tshangs pa'i theg pa ste /
NK041(di)035:90: de gnyis 'jig rten pa'i theg pa yin pas 'khor
NK041(di)035:91: ba las khyad par du 'dren mi nus pa'i phyir
NK041(di)035:93: theg pa 'di ni mkha' 'dra gzhal med khang chen te //
NK041(di)035:94: dga' skyid bde ba mngon par thob byed theg pa'i mchog /
NK041(di)035:95: de gang zhon nas sems can thams cad mya ngan bzla //
NK041(di)035:96: zhes pa las gzhan du gyur pas na /
NK041(di)035:97: theg pa dngos ma yin mod kyi /
NK041(di)035:98: de lta na'ang yang dag pa'i lta ba dang ldan pas dge bcu'i las lam la spyod pa ni /
NK041(di)035:99: rnam grol gyi theg pa thams cad kyi gazhi'am sngon du 'gro ba yin pas /
NK041(di)035:102: dge ba bcu las brtsams nas ni //
NK041(di)035:103: de yi chos ni rab tu dbye //
NK041(di)035:105: slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang bas lam rim du /
NK041(di)035:106: gzhi yi theg pa dang por zhog /
NK041(di)035:108: rin chen phreng ba las kyang /
NK041(di)035:109: mi yi chos lugs legs spyad na //
NK041(di)035:110: lha yul bgrod pa thag mi ring //
NK041(di)035:111: lha dang mi yi them skas la //
NK041(di)035:113: ces pa ltar mngon mtha'i them skas la 'dzeg nas
NK041(di)035:114: bgrod bya'i gnas nges legs sam rnam par grol ba'i
NK041(di)035:115: theg pa dela'ang / snga 'gyur rang skad kyi dbang du byas na /
NK041(di)035:116: spyi mdo dgongs pa 'dus pa las /
NK041(di)035:117: lang+ka'i bdag po gzhan yang gang //
NK041(di)035:118: don dam nges pa'i theg pa ni //
NK041(di)035:119: gsum du nges par bstan pa ste //
NK041(di)035:121: dbang bsgyur thabs kyi theg pa'o //
NK041(di)035:122: zhes gsum du snang ba las /
NK041(di)035:123: re re la'ang gsum gsum du phye bas theg pa
NK041(di)035:124: dgur 'gyur te kun 'byung 'dren pa'i theg pa ni
NK041(di)035:127: byang sems te mtshan nyid sde gsum dang /
NK041(di)035:128: dka' thub rig byed kyi theg pa ni kri ya /
NK041(di)035:130: yo ga ste phyi rgyud sde gsum dang /
NK041(di)035:131: dbang bsgyur thabs kyi theg pa ni /
NK041(di)035:132: bskyed pa ma h+aa yo ga /
NK041(di)035:134: man ngag a ti yo ga ste nang rgyud sde gsum rnams su dbyer yod cing /
NK041(di)035:135: gsum mam dgur phye ba de yang bsdu na /
NK041(di)035:137: theg pa rnam pa gnyis yin te //
NK041(di)035:138: mtshan nyid rgyu yi theg pa dang //
NK041(di)035:140: zhes pas rgyu pha rol tu phyin pa'i theg pa dang /
NK041(di)035:141: 'bras bu sngags kyi theg pa gnyis su 'du zhing /
NK041(di)035:143: sngags dang sbyor ba'i bya ba gtso bor ston pa dang mi ston pa'i khyad par te /
NK041(di)035:145: mdo dang sngags kyi khyad par ni //
NK041(di)035:146: cho ga'i bya ba yod med yin //
NK041(di)035:147: zhes pa'ang don 'di la dgongs par snang ngo //
NK041(di)035:148: 'o na pha rol du phyin pa'i tshul las sngags
NK041(di)035:149: kyi tshul gang gis khyad par du 'phags snyam na
NK041(di)035:151: sngags mchog tu gyur pa ste /
NK041(di)035:155: thabs la mkhas pa'i khyad par ro //
NK041(di)035:157: phar phyiin theg pas rang lam gyi byang chub thob pa la bskal pa grangs med thogs mod /
NK041(di)035:159: kri yas mi tshe bdun nam bskal pa brgyad /
NK041(di)035:160: u pa yas mi tshe lnga'am bskal pa gcig gam gsum /
NK041(di)035:161: yo gas tshe lo brgya pa'i mi'i skye ba gsum mam bcu drug /
NK041(di)035:162: bla med kyis skye ba 'adi'am bar dor byang chub thob par gsungs shing /
NK041(di)035:163: de ltar myur ba'i rgyu yang /
NK041(di)035:165: cho ga'i khyad par gyis lha rnams dngos su mchod pa len pa dang /
NK041(di)035:166: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad kyang
NK041(di)035:167: bla ma'i sku la zhugs nas sgrub pa po'i mchod
NK041(di)035:168: pa len pa sogs pas yongs su spyad pa las
NK041(di)035:169: byung ba'i bsod nams yod pa dang /
NK041(di)035:171: chu thig re yang gang+g+aa'i rdul snyed du 'phel bas /
NK041(di)035:172: de snyed kyi bsod nams 'byung ba dang /
NK041(di)035:173: ma dag pa'i snang ba 'gog pa'i zhing sbyong ba'i
NK041(di)035:174: ting nge 'dzin las dang po pa'i dus nas kyang
NK041(di)035:176: sngags dang phyag rgya ting nge 'dzin gyi khyad par
NK041(di)035:177: re res kyang sems can mtha' yas pa smin pa'i
NK041(di)035:178: rgyu khyad par can byed nus pa de dag sngags
NK041(di)035:179: kyi theg pa la zhugs tsam nyid nas yod pa'i
NK041(di)035:182: lus sems la tshor ba rtsub po med pa ste /
NK041(di)035:183: de'i rgyu yang 'di las skal pa drug gi lus kyang tshegs med pa grub pa dang /
NK041(di)035:184: rdzu 'phrul dang ting nge 'dzin mang po thob pa dang /
NK041(di)035:185: sngags kyi mthus de bzhin gshegs pa rnams mngon du
NK041(di)035:186: bzhugs shing 'gro ba'i bsam pa thams cad sgrub nus
NK041(di)035:187: pa'i rgyus bde ba yin no //
NK041(di)035:188: gsum pa thabs la mkhas pa ni /
NK041(di)035:189: rig pa 'dzin pa rnams dang tshul khrims mnyam pas lha dgyes pa dang /
NK041(di)035:190: spyod yul khyad par can dang 'brel ba'i ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK041(di)035:191: shes rab rmad du byung bas snod bcud dag mnyam chen por gtan la phebs pa dang /
NK041(di)035:192: spyod yul thams cad du lha dang sngags kyi thabs
NK041(di)035:193: la 'jug nus pas na thabs la mkhas pa yin
NK041(di)035:194: no // der ma zad pha rol tu phyin pa'i
NK041(di)035:195: rang lam gyis grangs med gsum gyi tshogs bsags pas
NK041(di)035:196: sa bcu pa'i byang chub sems dpa' sangs rgyas kyi
NK041(di)035:197: rgyal tshabs chen po'i go 'phang las lhag pa thob
NK041(di)035:198: no // mi nus kyang / skabs der sngags kyi
NK041(di)035:199: theg pa la zhugs nas rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas thob
NK041(di)035:200: dgos pas na sngags kyi theg pa ni bgrod pa
NK041(di)035:201: gcig pa'i lam du 'gyur ba'i phyir /
NK041(di)035:202: mthar thug gi theg pa gcig nyid du nges pas kyang 'phags te /
NK041(di)035:204: theg pa dpag med bstan pa yang //
NK041(di)035:205: ji ltar mos pa tha dad pas //
NK041(di)035:206: khrid par bya ba'i thabs su zad //
NK041(di)035:207: rdo rje theg pa nyid las med //
NK041(di)035:210: sa rnams khyad par bkod pa yang //
NK041(di)035:211: gsang ba'i snying por 'gro ba'i lam //
NK041(di)035:213: sgyu 'phrul brgyad cu pa las kyang //
NK041(di)035:214: mnyam nyid don rtogs rang rig rgyal po ni //
NK041(di)035:215: rgya mtsho chen por chu klung kun 'bab ltar //
NK041(di)035:216: bla med don rtogs thabs chen 'di dag tu //
NK041(di)035:217: rnam thar theg pa bsam yas ma lus 'dus //
NK041(di)035:219: 'o na gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa sde snod gsum gang du 'du zhe na /
NK041(di)035:220: dgongs pa mi mthun pa yang mang ste /
NK041(di)035:221: gang dag mngon pa'i sde snod las phyi nang gnyis las sngags ni nang gi mngon pa'o //
NK041(di)035:223: zab mo'i don mdor bsdus te ston pas na mdo sde'o zhes bzhed pa'ang yod mod /
NK041(di)035:224: rang lugs ni rig pa 'dzin pa'i sde snod ces /
NK041(di)035:225: sde snod gsum las legs par rkang thub pa gcig tu byas te /
NK041(di)035:226: sde snod bzhi par bzhag na legs par mngon no //
NK041(di)035:228: kun byed rgyal po'i rgyud las /
NK041(di)035:229: 'dod chags 'dul ba'i gnyen por gsungs pa ni //
NK041(di)035:230: 'dul ba'i sde snod nyi khri chig stong gsungs //
NK041(di)035:231: zhe sdang 'dul ba'i gnyen por gsungs pa ni //
NK041(di)035:232: mdo sde'i sde snod nyi khri chig stong gsungs //
NK041(di)035:233: gti mug 'dul ba'i gnyen por gsungs pa ni //
NK041(di)035:234: mngon pa'i sde snod nyi khri chig stong gsungs //
NK041(di)035:235: thams cad 'dul ba'i gnyen por gsungs pa ni //
NK041(di)035:236: sde snod bzhi pa nyi khri chig stong gsungs //
NK041(di)035:238: dpung bzang gis zhus pa las kyang /
NK041(di)035:239: bye ba phrag gsum dang ni 'bum phrag lnga //
NK041(di)035:240: rig 'dzin sde snod du ni rgyal bas gsungs //
NK041(di)035:242: slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang bas mdzad pa'i rnam 'joms kyi gzungs 'grel las /
NK041(di)035:243: sangs rgyas mchog gis chos gsungs pa //
NK041(di)035:244: 'dul ba mdo sde mngon pa dang //
NK041(di)035:245: rig pa 'dzin pa'i sde bzhir gnas //
NK041(di)035:247: rdo rje theg pa'i sde snod dang /
NK041(di)035:248: rig pa 'dzin pa'i sde snod dang /
NK041(di)035:251: chos 'di pa rnams kyi rgyud ces pa rnams ming gi rnam grangs so //
NK041(di)035:252: de la sngags kyi mtshan gzhi ni /
NK041(di)035:253: sbyang gzhi dbyings rang bzhin gyis rnam pa dag pa dang /
NK041(di)035:254: de la brten pa'i chos sbyang bya sbyong byed dang bcas pa thams cad yin zhing /
NK041(di)035:255: de yang sbyang gzhi la brten pa'i sbyang bya glo bur gyi dri ma rnams /
NK041(di)035:256: dbang gis rgyud smin par byas nas /
NK041(di)035:257: de dang rjes su 'brel ba'i sgo nas lam bsgom pa dang /
NK041(di)035:258: des bral thob kyi yon tan gyi char gtogs pa rnams sbyong byed yin no //
NK041(di)035:259: de ltar sbyangs pas dbyings la sgrib byed kyi dri ma phra rags thams cad dag nas /
NK041(di)035:260: gzhi'i yon tan ji lta ba bzhin mngon du gyur pa ni 'bras bu ste /
NK041(di)035:261: de skad du'ang gsang ba grub pa las /
NK041(di)035:262: dbyings la bral ba dag thob 'bras //
NK041(di)035:263: gsang sngags rnam pa bzhir bshad de //
NK041(di)035:266: chos kyi dbyings rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag pa dang /
NK041(di)035:267: rjod byed thugs rdo rje'i gsang ba 'khor dang bcas pa ste /
NK041(di)035:269: sngags rnams kun gyi mtshan nyid ni //
NK041(di)035:270: sangs rgyas kun gyi thugs yin te //
NK041(di)035:271: chos kyi snying po sgrub byed pa //
NK041(di)035:272: chos kyi dbyings dang yang dag ldan //
NK041(di)035:275: man+t+ra zhes pa'i sgra las drangs na /
NK041(di)035:276: yid shes bde myur du skyob pas na sngags te /
NK041(di)035:277: gsang 'dus kyi rgyud phyi ma las /
NK041(di)035:278: ma na yid ces bya ba ste //
NK041(di)035:279: tra ni skyob par bya ba'i don //
NK041(di)035:281: gsang sngags kyi dbye ba ni /
NK041(di)035:282: gsar rnying thun mong gi bzhed pa'i dbang du byas na bzhir bzung ste /
NK041(di)035:283: rdo rje snying po bkod pa'i rgyud las /
NK041(di)035:284: bde bar gshegs pas dgongs pa'i rgyud //
NK041(di)035:285: rnam pa bzhi ru yang dag bshad //
NK041(di)035:286: bya spyod rnal 'byor bla med do //
NK041(di)035:288: de yang bzhir 'byed pa'i rgyu mtshan ni lnga las /
NK041(di)035:289: dang po mi rigs bzhi'i spyod pa la dgongs nas /
NK041(di)035:290: de 'dul ba'i phyir bzhir gsungs te /
NK041(di)035:291: dur khrod rgyan gyi rgyud las /
NK041(di)035:292: bram ze rgyal rigs rje'u rigs dang //
NK041(di)035:293: rmangs rigs gdol pa 'dul don du //
NK041(di)035:294: rgyud ni rnam pa bzhir gsungs te //
NK041(di)035:295: bya spyod rnal 'byor bla med do //
NK041(di)035:297: gnyis pa gang zag gi blo rigs bzhi la dgongs nas kyang bzhir gsungs te /
NK041(di)035:299: sems can dman la bya ba'i rgyud //
NK041(di)035:300: de lhag rnams la spyod pa'i rgyud //
NK041(di)035:301: sems can mchog la rnal 'byor rgyud //
NK041(di)035:302: de lhag rnams la bla med rgyud //
NK041(di)035:304: gsum pa rdzogs ldan la sogs pa'i dus bzhi la dgongs nas kyang bzhir gsungs te /
NK041(di)035:305: dpal phreng dam pa'i rgyud las /
NK041(di)035:306: gsang sngags byung tshul rnam bzhi ste //
NK041(di)035:307: bskal pa rdzogs ldan gsum ldan gnyis //
NK041(di)035:308: rtsod dus rgyud kyang de bzhin du //
NK041(di)035:309: gdul bya'i ngo la snang ba yin //
NK041(di)035:311: bzhi pa sbyang gzhi 'dod chags kyi 'jug tshul bzhi la dgongs nas kyang bzhir gsungs te /
NK041(di)035:313: bltas dang dgod dang lag bcang dang //
NK041(di)035:314: 'khyud dang gnyis sprod la sogs pa'i //
NK041(di)035:315: rgyud kyang rnam pa bzhir gsungs so //
NK041(di)035:317: lnga pa lha bzhi'i rjes su 'jug pa'i phyin ci
NK041(di)035:318: log bzhi drangs pa la dgongs nas kyang bzhir gsungs
NK041(di)035:319: te / gti mug can tshangs pa gtsang sbra chos
NK041(di)035:320: su smra ba rjes su 'dzin pa'i phyir bya ba'i
NK041(di)035:321: te / rgyud / zhe sdang can khyab 'jug 'tshe
NK041(di)035:322: ba chos su smra ba rjes su 'dzin pa'i phyir
NK041(di)035:323: te / rgyud / spyod rgyud / nga rgyal can
NK041(di)035:324: brgya byin 'byor pa chos su smra ba rjes su
NK041(di)035:326: 'dod chags can dbang phyug 'dod chags chos su smra
NK041(di)035:327: ba rjes su 'dzin pa'i phyir rnal 'byor bla na
NK041(di)035:328: med pa'i rgyud gsungs pa yin la /
NK041(di)035:329: de rnams brjod bya rjod byed sogs re re nas
NK041(di)035:330: gtan la phab na mtha' yas par 'gyur pa'i phyir
NK041(di)035:331: re zhig de tsam byas nas /
NK041(di)035:334: bya rgyud kyi dbang rjes gnang lta bu yin na 'di skad ces /
NK041(di)035:335: kri ya zhes pa'i sgra las drangs na bya ba'i rgyud de /
NK041(di)035:336: bsam gtan phyi ma'i 'grel pa las /
NK041(di)035:337: rgyud 'di ni lus ngag gi bya ba gtso bor ston pas bya ba'i rgyud do //
NK041(di)035:340: don dam pa mtha' bzhi dang bral ba'i rtogs pas /
NK041(di)035:341: kun rdzob tu dngos grub gzhan la re zhing rtsol ba'i thabs su gyur pa ste /
NK041(di)035:342: slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang bas sgyu 'phrul lam rim du /
NK041(di)035:343: gnyis med mnyam pa ma shes pas //
NK041(di)035:344: don dam dag pa chos nyid tsam //
NK041(di)035:345: ye shes bzhi yon kun rdzob lha //
NK041(di)035:346: res bsgom bya ba las kyis //
NK041(di)035:348: de ji ltar nyams su len tshul ni /
NK041(di)035:350: chu yi dbang bskur dbu rgyan dang //
NK041(di)035:351: bya ba'i rgyud la rab tu grags //
NK041(di)035:352: zhes pas chu dang cod pan gyi dbang tsam bskur bas rgyud snod rung du bsgrubs nas /
NK041(di)035:353: dka' thub dang gtsang sbra'i spyod pa la gnas pas /
NK041(di)035:354: mdun bskyed kyi lha spyan drangs pa la mchod cing /
NK041(di)035:355: dam tshig gi phyag rgyas btab /
NK041(di)035:356: bzlas pas thugs brgyud bskul ba'i bsnyen pa rnams lha
NK041(di)035:357: dang mi dang rje khol gyi tshul du bltas nas
NK041(di)035:359: rig pa thams cad kyi dngos grub len pa'i rgyud las /
NK041(di)035:360: rje dpon rgyal po'i skur bltas la //
NK041(di)035:361: rang nyid bran gyi 'du shes kyis //
NK041(di)035:362: sngags sgrub dngos grub snying po ni //
NK041(di)035:363: bla na med pa'i mchog tu blang //
NK041(di)035:365: 'di'i rang lam gyis dbang po rno ba ni mi tshe bdun nam /
NK041(di)035:366: ji ltar 'gyang na'ang bskal pa chen po brgyad nas byang chub thob par bzhed pa yin no //
NK041(di)035:367: de yang bya ba'i rgyud la dbye na rigs drug /
NK041(di)035:368: de la gtso bo'i rigs gsum ni /
NK041(di)035:369: de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs dang //
NK041(di)035:374: lngas tsan nam rgyas pa'i rigs /
NK041(di)035:375: 'jig rten pa'i rigs rnams te drug las /
NK041(di)035:376: de bzhin rigs kyi skabs yin la /
NK041(di)035:377: 'dir de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs la brgyad de /
NK041(di)035:379: rigs kyi bdag po'i rigs kyi 'khor los sgyur ba dang /
NK041(di)035:382: rigs kyi khro bo khro mo dang /
NK041(di)035:383: rigs kyi pho nya mo dang /
NK041(di)035:385: rigs kyi 'jig rten dang brgyad las /
NK041(di)035:386: 'dir rigs kyi gtso bo'i rgyud thub pa dam tshig gsum bkod dang /
NK041(di)035:387: rigs kyi bdag po'i rgyud 'jam dpal dbyangs 'di zhes bya ba'i rig gtad dam /
NK041(di)035:389: dkyil 'khor du 'jug cing dbang bskur bsgrub par byed pa skabs su bab pa yin /
NK041(di)035:390: de yang rdo rje slob dpon gyi bgyi 'os rnams chad lhag med pa sngon du song grub pas /
NK041(di)035:391: da khyed rang rnams kyi ngo skal du gyur pa la /
NK041(di)035:392: bla ma dang lhag pa'i lha dbyer ma mchis pa'i drung du rig gtad dam /
NK041(di)035:395: dbang zhu ba'i yon du man+dala phul mdzod /
NK041(di)035:396: ces pa'i sgyur tshul rnams 'og ma rnams la 'gre shes par bya'o //
NK041(di)035:397: yang bya rgyud pad rigs la mtshon na /
NK041(di)035:402: rigs kyi khro bo dang khro mo dang /
NK041(di)035:403: rigs kyi bka' nyan pho mo dang lnga las /
NK041(di)035:404: 'dir rigs kyi gtso bo'i rgyud tshe dang ye shes dpag tu med pa'am /
NK041(di)035:405: rigs kyi bdag po'i rgyud 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs 'di zhes bya ba'i rgyud rig gtad dam /
NK041(di)035:408: yang rdo rje'i rigs la mtshon na /
NK041(di)035:409: 'dir rdo rje'i rigs la lnga ste /
NK041(di)035:413: rigs kyi khro bo dang khro mo dang /
NK041(di)035:414: rigs kyi bka' nyan pho nya phyag brnyan dang lnga las /
NK041(di)035:415: 'dir rigs kyi gtso bo'i rgyud mi 'khrugs pa'am /
NK041(di)035:416: rigs kyi bdag po'i rgyud phyag na rdo rje'am /
NK041(di)035:417: rdo rje rnam par 'joms pa 'di zhes bya ba'i rig gtad dam /
NK041(di)035:419: de tsam gyis mtshon par byas nas bya rgyud kyi rigs lhag ma rnams la'ang sbyor shes par bya'o //
NK041(di)035:420: yang gnyis ka'i rgyud dam spyod rgyud kyi dbang rjes gnang lta bu yin na /
NK041(di)035:423: u pa ya zhes pa'i sgra las drangs na gnyis ka'am spyod pa'i rgyud de /
NK041(di)035:425: lta ba yo gar lta ba la //
NK041(di)035:426: spyod pa kri yar spyod pa'o //
NK041(di)035:427: de phyir gnyis ka'i rgyud ces grags //
NK041(di)035:429: rnam snang mngon byang gi don bsdus las /
NK041(di)035:430: rgyud 'di ni lus ngag gi bya ba dang /
NK041(di)035:431: ting nge 'dzin gnyis ka spyod pas spyod pa'i rgyud do //
NK041(di)035:434: lta sgom yo ga dang spyod pa bya ba dang
NK041(di)035:435: cha 'drar spyod pas dngos grub sgrub pa'i thabs su
NK041(di)035:436: gyur pa ste / lta phreng las /
NK041(di)035:437: gnyis ka la brten pa las grub pa'o //
NK041(di)035:439: de ji ltar nyams su len pa'i tshul ni /
NK041(di)035:441: rdo rje dril bu de bzhin ming //
NK041(di)035:442: spyod pa'i rgyud du rab tu gsal //
NK041(di)035:443: zhes chu cod pan gyi steng du /
NK041(di)035:445: ming dbang rnams bskur bas snod rung du byas nas
NK041(di)035:446: spyod pa phal cher bya ba dang 'dra ba las
NK041(di)035:447: / lta sgom yo ga dang mthun pas nyams len gyi tshe yang /
NK041(di)035:448: bdag dam tshig pa dang lha ye shes pa spun
NK041(di)035:449: nam grogs po'i tshul du bzang ngan med par bltas
NK041(di)035:450: te / mchod bstod bzlas pa la sogs pa'i sgo nas dngos grub len pa yin no //
NK041(di)035:451: de ltar yang lta rim las /
NK041(di)035:452: gnyis ka'i rgyud kyi 'dod pa ni //
NK041(di)035:453: lta spyod gong 'og rjes su mthun //
NK041(di)035:455: de yang sgom pa yo ga dang rjes su mthun rgyu ni /
NK041(di)035:456: yo ga dam ye gnyis phan tshun grogs po lta spyod rgyud dang thun mong ba dang /
NK041(di)035:457: thun min dam ye gnyis med du byed pa gnyis las /
NK041(di)035:460: lha dang rnal 'byor bdag nyid kyang //
NK041(di)035:461: spun dang grogs po'i tshul du 'dod //
NK041(di)035:462: ces yo ga'i 'dod gzhung 'chad pa'i tshe gsungs pa ltar ro //
NK041(di)035:463: de ltar 'bad pas dbang po yang rab mi tshe lnga'am /
NK041(di)035:464: 'gyang na'ang bskal pa gcig gam gsum gyis rang 'bras thob par bzhed pa yin /
NK041(di)035:465: de yang spyod pa'i rgyud la dbye na /
NK041(di)035:466: sku gsung thugs kyi rigs gsum las /
NK041(di)035:467: 'dir sku'i rigs rnam par snang mdzad mngon par byang chub pa /
NK041(di)035:468: 'phags pa mi g.yo ba 'di zhes bya ba'i rjes gnang ngam /
NK041(di)035:470: thugs kyi rigs phyag na rdo rje 'di zhes bya ba'i /
NK041(di)035:472: yang rnal 'byor gyi rgyud kyi dbang lta bu yin na /
NK041(di)035:475: yo ga zhes pa'i sgra las drangs na /
NK041(di)035:476: nang gi rnal 'byor gtso bor byed pa'i sgo nas ston pas na rnal 'byor rgyud ces bya ste /
NK041(di)035:477: de kho na nyid snang ba'i don bsdus las /
NK041(di)035:478: rgyud 'di ni ting nge 'dzin gtso bor ston pas rnal 'byor gyi rgyud do //
NK041(di)035:481: don dam mtshan ma med pa'i chos nyid kyii byin rlabs kun rdzob lhar btags te /
NK041(di)035:482: rtog pa bzang ngan blang dor gyi rtsol bas 'bras bu bsgrub pa ste /
NK041(di)035:483: sangs rgyas gsang ba'i lam rim las /
NK041(di)035:484: lhun grub mnyam pa ma mthong bas //
NK041(di)035:485: chos kun rnam dag ye shes kyis //
NK041(di)035:486: byin rlabs rdo rje dbyings sprul pa //
NK041(di)035:487: blang dor phyed pa rnal 'byor ro //
NK041(di)035:489: de ji ltar nyams su len tshul ni //
NK041(di)035:491: phyir mi ldog pa bum pa'i dbang //
NK041(di)035:492: rnal 'byor rgyud du gsal bar byas //
NK041(di)035:493: de ni drug pa'i bye brag dbang //
NK041(di)035:494: de ni slob dpon dbang zhes bya //
NK041(di)035:499: rdo rje slob dpon gyi dbang /
NK041(di)035:500: rjes gnang sogs mtha' brten dang bcas pa bskur bas snod rung du byas nas /
NK041(di)035:501: bdag bskyed dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor lo phyag rgya bzhi'i rgyas btab nas bsgom zhing /
NK041(di)035:502: thun mthar phyag rgya bkrol nas gshegs su gsol /
NK041(di)035:503: de yang mngon byang lnga dang cho 'phrul bzhi'i sgo
NK041(di)035:504: nas lha'i rnal 'byor phyag rgya bzhi ldan du bsgom
NK041(di)035:505: zhing / yo ga khyad par ba la spyod rgyud
NK041(di)035:506: dang thun mong ma yin pa'i dam ye gnyis med
NK041(di)035:507: du byas nas dngos grub len pa ste /
NK041(di)035:509: gnyis su med pa'i chos nyid ngang //
NK041(di)035:510: bla med dngos grub dam pa blang //
NK041(di)035:512: de ltar 'bad pas tshe lo brgya pa'i mi'i skye ba gsum mam /
NK041(di)035:513: tha na'ang bcu drug gi yun tshad tsam la dbang
NK041(di)035:514: po rno shos kyis phyag rgya chen po'i dngos grub
NK041(di)035:515: 'grub cing / de'i yun tshad nyis 'gyur gyis sa bcu pa la sbyor ba yin gsungs /
NK041(di)035:516: de yang yo ga'i rgyud la dbye na /
NK041(di)035:518: bshad rgyud rtse mo dang dpal mchog /
NK041(di)035:519: cha mthun gyi rgyud ngan song sbyong ba sogs dang /
NK041(di)035:520: thabs shes kyi sgo nas phye na /
NK041(di)035:521: pha rgyud de nyid 'dus pa dang rtse mo sogs /
NK041(di)035:522: ma rgyud dpal mchog dang po dang rdo rje snying rgyan sogs yod pa las /
NK041(di)035:523: rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor du 'jug cing dbang bskur ba sogs /
NK041(di)035:525: cha mthun gyi rgyud ngan song thams cad yongs su
NK041(di)035:526: spyong ba gzi brjid kyi rgyal po kun rig rnam
NK041(di)035:527: par snang mdzad kyi dkyil 'khor du /
NK041(di)035:529: ngan song sbyong ba gzi brjid kyi rgyal po brtag
NK041(di)035:530: pa phyogs gcig pa las byung ba gtsug dgu'i dkyil
NK041(di)035:532: yang rnal 'byor bla med kyi skabs yin na /
NK041(di)035:535: ma h+aa yo ga zhes pa'i sgra las drangs na rnal 'byor chen po ste /
NK041(di)035:536: gnyis med kyi don la blo 'byor pas /
NK041(di)035:537: yo ga phyi ma las ches khyad par du 'phags pa'i phyir ro //
NK041(di)035:539: bskyed rdzogs zung 'jug gi sgo nas 'khor 'das mnyam
NK041(di)035:540: nyid kyi don la rtogs goms kyi sbyor bas grol
NK041(di)035:541: ba thob pa'i rang bzhin no //
NK041(di)035:542: 'di ni theg pa 'og ma rnams kun rdzob rdzas
NK041(di)035:543: yod dang btags yod du bzung nas bzang ngan blang
NK041(di)035:544: dor du blta ba las 'phags te /
NK041(di)035:545: 'dir chos rnams la mi gnyis kyi bsam spyod dang ldan pas /
NK041(di)035:546: 'bras bu'i ngo bor snang stong zung 'jug gi chos skur rtogs par byas nas /
NK041(di)035:547: de dang rjes su mthun pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyis goms par byed pa'i phyir te /
NK041(di)035:548: slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang bas /
NK041(di)035:549: thabs kyi theg pa chen por ni //
NK041(di)035:550: rnam par byang dang sdug bsngal dag /
NK041(di)035:551: kun rdzob tu yang dbyer med de //
NK041(di)035:552: lta ba mtho dman de tsam mo //
NK041(di)035:554: de ji ltar nyams su len pa'i khyad par yang /
NK041(di)035:556: rnal 'byor bla ma yi ni mtshan //
NK041(di)035:557: gsang ba yi ni dbang rgyal bshad //
NK041(di)035:558: shes rab ye shes bla na med //
NK041(di)035:559: bzhi pa de yang de bzhin no //
NK041(di)035:561: sgyu 'phrul rtsa rgyud phyi ma las /
NK041(di)035:562: slob dpon gsang ba shes rab dang //
NK041(di)035:563: de ma thag pa bzhi pa ste //
NK041(di)035:564: zhes bum dbang gi steng du /
NK041(di)035:565: thun mong ma yin pa mchog dbang gong ma gsum
NK041(di)035:566: bsnan nas bzhi bskur bas snod rung du byas nas
NK041(di)035:567: / lam bskyed rim ma dag pa'i snang ba dbyings
NK041(di)035:568: su sbyong ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor lo bsgom zhing
NK041(di)035:569: / / dbang dang bskyed rim gnyis ka la yang 'bras bu'i bzhugs tshul dang /
NK041(di)035:570: rnam pa mthun pa'i lam du byed tshul dang /
NK041(di)035:571: mar 'khor ba dang rnam pa mthun pa'i dri ma sbyong tshul te /
NK041(di)035:576: thun mtshams su yang snang ba thams cad lha dang lha mor bsgom /
NK041(di)035:577: rdzogs rim rdo rje'i lus la gnad du bsnun pa'i thabs kyis /
NK041(di)035:580: rlung rnams dbu mar thiim pas mngon du gyur pa'i bde stong zung 'jug 'grub /
NK041(di)035:581: spyod pa rnam pa gsum gyi nye rgyus 'bras bu la sbyor bar bzhed /
NK041(di)035:582: de yang bsam pa'i stobs che ba gcig gis 'bad pas bsgom na /
NK041(di)035:583: tshe lo brgya ba'i tshe gang gcig gi yun la
NK041(di)035:584: lo gzhan la ma ltos par 'tshang rgya nus par
NK041(di)035:585: gsungs / de lta bu'i rnal 'byor bla na med pa la dbye na /
NK041(di)035:586: gangs can ljongs 'dir gsang sngags gsar rnying lugs srol gnyis byung /
NK041(di)035:587: de gnyis kyi khyad par ni /
NK041(di)035:588: lo ts+aa ba rin chen bzang po ma byon gong du 'gyur ba'i mdo rgyud rnams snga 'gyur dang /
NK041(di)035:589: de phyin 'gyur ba rnams gsar ma yin zhes bzhed de /
NK041(di)035:590: gtso che'i dbang du byas nas gsungs pa yin /
NK041(di)035:593: de ltar gsar rnying gnyis las /
NK041(di)035:596: skyes pa rnams ni gdul bya'i phyir //
NK041(di)035:597: rnal 'byor pha yi rgyud bstan cing //
NK041(di)035:598: btsun mo rnams ni dga' bya'i phyir //
NK041(di)035:599: phyi nas rnal 'byor ma rgyud gsungs //
NK041(di)035:602: gnyis med gnyis su med par ston //
NK041(di)035:606: gnyis su med pa'i snying po don gyi rgyud dang gsum /
NK041(di)035:607: de rnams kyi khyad par ni /
NK041(di)035:608: dkyil 'khor gang du lha pho'i rnam pa mang zhing
NK041(di)035:609: dar ras rin po che'i rgyan can sogs yab kyi
NK041(di)035:610: lha sngags cho ga nyid rtsal 'don du byung na
NK041(di)035:611: pha rgyud / gang du lha mo'i rnam pa mang
NK041(di)035:612: zhing gcer bur rus pa'i rgyan can sogs dang yum
NK041(di)035:613: gyi lha sngags cho ga sogs rtsal 'don du byung
NK041(di)035:614: pha rgyud / na ma rgyud / yang thabs kyi
NK041(di)035:615: de kho na nyid rgya che bar ston pa pha
NK041(di)035:616: pha rgyud / na ma rgyud / rgyud / shes
NK041(di)035:617: rab kyi de kho na nyid zab par ston pa
NK041(di)035:618: pha rgyud / na ma rgyud / rgyud / ma
NK041(di)035:619: rgyud / de dag cha mnyam par ston na gnyis
NK041(di)035:620: pha rgyud / na ma rgyud / rgyud / ma
NK041(di)035:621: rgyud / med do // zhes gsungs kyang gtso bor
NK041(di)035:622: ni bla med kyi thun mong ma yin pa mchog
NK041(di)035:623: dbang gong ma gsum gyi nyams len gang rtsal du
NK041(di)035:624: bton nas nyams su len pas bzhag pa nyid legs
NK041(di)035:625: pha rgyud / na ma rgyud / rgyud / ma
NK041(di)035:626: rgyud / med do // par snang ste / des
NK041(di)035:627: na gang du gsang dbang gi lam steng sgo rlung
NK041(di)035:628: gi rnal 'byor gtso bor ston pa pha rgyud /
NK041(di)035:629: gang du shes rab ye shes kyi lam 'og sgo
NK041(di)035:630: las rgya'i rnal 'byor gtso bor ston pa ma rgyud
NK041(di)035:631: / gang du dbang bzhi pa'i lam phyag rdzogs kyi
NK041(di)035:632: rnal 'byor gtso bor ston pa gnyis med kyi rgyud
NK041(di)035:633: / do // de gsum gyi mtshan gzhi yang /
NK041(di)035:634: pha rgyud gsang 'dus dang dmar nag 'jigs gsum sogs /
NK041(di)035:638: gnyis med kyi rgyud dus kyi 'khor lo la sogs pa'o //
NK041(di)035:639: bdag nyid chen po sa skya pa ni kye rdor
NK041(di)035:640: gyi rgyud kyang gnyis med kyi rgyud du 'dzin cing
NK041(di)035:642: gur nas ma rgyud bcu bzhi'i nang du drangs pa dang /
NK041(di)035:643: rnal 'byor ma rgyud kye rdo rje //
NK041(di)035:644: zhes sogs kyis gnod pas ma rgyud du 'thad ces gsungs pa'ang snang /
NK041(di)035:645: pha rgyud 'dus pa lta bu la dper mtshon na /
NK041(di)035:646: de las 'dir sgron ma gsal bar /
NK041(di)035:647: thub pa chen pos chos phung po //
NK041(di)035:648: brgyad khri bzhi stong gang gsungs pa //
NK041(di)035:650: de bas 'di ni rgyud kun rtse //
NK041(di)035:651: zhes mdo sde dang rgyud thams cad kyi snod dang
NK041(di)035:652: rtsa bar gsungs pa dpal gsang ba 'dus pa'i dkyil
NK041(di)035:653: 'khor du / zhes pa lta bu'i so so'i che ba re brjod nas /
NK041(di)035:654: 'di dang 'di zhes bya ba'i dkyil 'khor du zhes /
NK041(di)035:657: gnyis med kyi rgyud thams cad la rigs 'gre shes par bya zhing /
NK041(di)035:658: de dag la lhag gnas dang /
NK041(di)035:659: 'jug pa sogs skabs thob phyed par bya /
NK041(di)035:660: yang dbang bzhi'i don tshang yang dbang gi cho ga dngos ma yin cing /
NK041(di)035:661: cho ga'i rim pa shin tu zor yang ba rnams byin rlabs zhes grags pa ltar /
NK041(di)035:663: sku gsung thugs kyi rjes su gnang ba sogs skabs bab kyis bsgyur ba'i 'phrul zhes par bya'o //
NK041(di)035:664: yang gsang sngags rnying ma'i skabs yin na /
NK041(di)035:665: gtso che'i dbang du byas nas gsungs pa yin /
NK041(di)035:667: de ltar gsar rnying gnyis las /
NK041(di)035:668: 'dir gsar ma las khyad par du gyur pa gsang sngags rnying ma yin /
NK041(di)035:669: de yang gang gis khyad par du gyur ce na /
NK041(di)035:670: lo ts+aa ba chen po rong zom chos kyi bzang po'i zhal snga nas /
NK041(di)035:671: gsang sngags rnying ma ba rnams la gsar ma las khyad par du 'phags pa'i che ba drug yod /
NK041(di)035:673: dang po spyan 'dren yon bdag gi che ba ni /
NK041(di)035:674: snga 'gyur gyi yon bdag 'phags pa rigs gsum mgon
NK041(di)035:675: po rnam pa rgyal po'i tshul bzung ba mnga' bdag
NK041(di)035:676: mes dbon rnam gsum yin pas phyi 'gyur ba rnams
NK041(di)035:678: gnyis pa gang du bsgyur zhing gtan la phab pa'i gnas ni /
NK041(di)035:679: sngon sprul pa'i gtsug lag khang bsam yas sogs chos 'khor stod smad du yin pas /
NK041(di)035:680: da lta'i dgon phag phug tu bsgyur ba dang mi 'dra /
NK041(di)035:681: gsum pa sgyur byed lo ts+aa'i khyad par ni /
NK041(di)035:682: sngon gyi lo ts+aa ba sgra bsgyur bee ro tsa na dang ska cog zhang gsum /
NK041(di)035:683: rma gnyags sogs sprul pa'i lo ts+aa ba rnams kyis bsgyur ba'i chos yin /
NK041(di)035:684: da lta'i lo ts+aa ba dbyar mang yul du bsdad /
NK041(di)035:685: dgun rgya bal du yug re phyin nas bsgyur ba dang mi 'dra /
NK041(di)035:686: bzhi pa pan+di ta'i khyad par ni /
NK041(di)035:687: sngon gyi pan+di ta mkhan po zhi ba 'tsho dang /
NK041(di)035:689: slob dpon chen po pad+ma 'byung gnas dang /
NK041(di)035:690: pan chen bi ma la mi tra sogs sangs rgyas dang /
NK041(di)035:691: sa chen po la bzhugs pa'i byang 'phags rnams kyi chos yin /
NK041(di)035:692: da lta'i gser 'tshol du 'khyams pa'i pan+di ta dang mi 'dra /
NK041(di)035:693: lnga pa zhu rten me tog gi khyad par ni /
NK041(di)035:694: sngon gser sha ba'i blud bu bkang ba dang /
NK041(di)035:695: bre la gzhal nas phul te zhus pa'i chos yin /
NK041(di)035:696: da lta mchan nas gser zho re re gnyis gnyis bton nas zhus pa dang mi 'dra /
NK041(di)035:697: drug pa chos kyi khyad par ni /
NK041(di)035:698: sngon 'phags yul du sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa grwa ma nyams pa'i dus su bsgyur ba ma zad /
NK041(di)035:699: 'phags yul na med pa'i rgyud dbang thob pa'i byang chub sems dpa' dang /
NK041(di)035:702: mkha' 'gro ma rnams kyis bzung ste dag pa'i zhing na bzhugs pa dang /
NK041(di)035:703: dzam bu'i gling gi cha shas sing+ga la dang /
NK041(di)035:704: nub phyogs o rgyan gyi yul sogs nas slob dpon
NK041(di)035:705: chen po pad+ma dang bi ma la sogs kyis rdzu
NK041(di)035:706: 'phrul gyi bkod pas blangs nas bsgyur bas rgya gar
NK041(di)035:707: du pan grub yongs la ma grags pa mang po
NK041(di)035:708: zhig kyang bod kyi bsod nams kyi skal bar byon
NK041(di)035:709: / 'gyur kyang sngon gyi lo ts+aa rnams sprul pa'i
NK041(di)035:710: sku yin pas don ji lta ba bzhin du gtan
NK041(di)035:711: la pheb pas go sla dbyings mjal ba la rlabs
NK041(di)035:712: / che / phyis lo ts+aa ba rnams kyis don
NK041(di)035:713: bsgyur ma nus pa rgya dpe'i go rim ltar sgra
NK041(di)035:714: 'gyur byas pas tshig sgrims pa la go dka' /
NK041(di)035:715: dbyings mjal ba la rlabs chung ba ltar snang bas mi 'dra ba yin no //
NK041(di)035:716: khyad par de ldan gyi gsang sngags rnying ma de la'ang /
NK041(di)035:719: zab mo dag snang ste brgyud pa'i bka' srol gsum du gnas shing /
NK041(di)035:720: de thams cad kyi brjod bya rjod byed spyi'i lus kyis phye na /
NK041(di)035:722: sgrub sde gnyis su 'dus pa las /
NK041(di)035:723: de'i dang po rgyud sde la'ang gsum ste rgyud ma h+aa yo ga /
NK041(di)035:725: man ngag a ti yo ga'o //
NK041(di)035:726: de gsum gyi khyad par la /
NK041(di)035:727: lha rje zur chung ba'i zhal nas /
NK041(di)035:728: rig pa'i cho 'phrul du snang ba ma h+aa /
NK041(di)035:729: rang rig rtsal du snang ba a nu /
NK041(di)035:730: rig pa rang snang a ti'o //
NK041(di)035:731: zhes gsungs pa'i dgongs pa ni /
NK041(di)035:732: chos thams cad sems nyid snang stong dbyer med kyi cho 'phrul du rtogs pas /
NK041(di)035:733: thabs bskyed pa'i rim pa dang spyod pa la gtso bor brten pa rgyud ma h+aa yo ga /
NK041(di)035:734: chos thams cad sems nyid dbyings ye shes gnyis su med pa'i rtsal du rtogs pas /
NK041(di)035:735: shes rab rdzogs pa'i rim pa dang ting nge 'dzin
NK041(di)035:736: la gtso bor brten pa lung a nu yo ga
NK041(di)035:737: / chos thams cad ye nas skye 'gag med pa'i
NK041(di)035:738: rang byung gi ye shes rang snang ba rtogs pas
NK041(di)035:739: / / ye thog tu grol bar byed pa'i thabs spang blang re dogs dang bral ba ste /
NK041(di)035:740: lta ba la gtso bor bsten pa'i rdzogs pa chen po a ti yo ga'o //
NK041(di)035:741: sgyu 'phrul zhi khro la mtshon na /
NK041(di)035:742: de las 'dir rgyud ma h+aa yo ga /
NK041(di)035:743: de la'ang bskyed rim thabs kyi cha dang /
NK041(di)035:744: rdzogs rim rlung gtso bor byed pa'i gsal stong rnam
NK041(di)035:745: par mi rtog pa'i tshul gyis nyams su len pa
NK041(di)035:746: ma h+aa'i ma h+aa ste pha rgyud gsang ba 'dus
NK041(di)035:748: bskyed rim gyi spros pa shas chung zhing shes rab
NK041(di)035:749: rdzogs pa'i rim pa khams byang chub kyi sems thig
NK041(di)035:750: le gtso bor byed pas bde stong rnam par mi
NK041(di)035:751: rtog pa'i tshul du nyams su len pa ma h+aa'i
NK041(di)035:752: a nu ste ma rgyud sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor dang
NK041(di)035:753: dpal yang dag la sogs pa dang /
NK041(di)035:755: de'ang rdzogs rim rtsa thig rlung gsum las skyes pa'i
NK041(di)035:756: bde gsal rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye shes dang
NK041(di)035:757: / khyad par 'od gsal ye shes chen po la
NK041(di)035:758: gtso bor byed pa'i tshul gyis nyams su len pa
NK041(di)035:759: ma h+aa'i a ti ste gnyis med kyi rgyud sgyu
NK041(di)035:760: 'phrul d+r+wa ba la sogs pa las /
NK041(di)035:761: 'dir snga 'gyur bka' ma'i bka' srol rdo rje sems
NK041(di)035:762: dpa' sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba zhi ba'am khro bo'i dkyil
NK041(di)035:763: 'khor du dbang bskur ba skabs su bab pa yin
NK041(di)035:764: / de la'ang thog mar nges shes 'dren pa bla
NK041(di)035:765: ma brgyud pa'i lo rgyus kyi dbang du byas na
NK041(di)035:767: rgyal ba sems dpa' rnal 'byor pa //
NK041(di)035:768: dgongs pa rig pa rna bar brgyud //
NK041(di)035:769: ces gsungs pa ltar gsum las /
NK041(di)035:770: dang po phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i sangs rgyas thams cad
NK041(di)035:771: kyi bdag nyid ston pa rigs drug pa bcom ldan
NK041(di)035:772: 'das dpal kun tu bzang pos 'og min chen po'i
NK041(di)035:773: gnas su / 'chad pa'i skyes bu de bzhin gshegs pa lnga yang rnam par snang bar mdzad nas /
NK041(di)035:774: rdo rje gsang ba la sogs pa rig pa khyad
NK041(di)035:775: par can gyi 'khor rnams la rgyud kyi rgyal po
NK041(di)035:777: dus rtag pa rgyun gyi 'khor lor ston pa ni rgyal ba dgongs brgyud do //
NK041(di)035:778: rgyal sras sems dpa'i 'khor gyi nang nas rigs gsum
NK041(di)035:779: mgon pos lha klu gnod sbyin gyi gnas su bshad
NK041(di)035:781: thub pa'i dbang po mya ngan las 'das nas lo nyi shu rtsa brgyad na /
NK041(di)035:782: lang+ka'i yul te sing ga la'i gling gi ri bo
NK041(di)035:783: ma la ya'am deng sang su ma na ku ta'i
NK041(di)035:784: ri zhes grags pa'i rtse mor gsang bdag gis /
NK041(di)035:785: dam pa'i rigs can d+r+wa ma lnga la bshad pa rnams ni rig 'dzin brda brgyud do //
NK041(di)035:786: de nas gang zag snyan brgyud ni /
NK041(di)035:787: gsang bdag gis rigs can lnga la chos 'khor bskor
NK041(di)035:788: ba'i byin rlabs kyis za hor gyi rgyal po dzahl
NK041(di)035:789: rmi ltas ngo mtshar ba bdun rmis shing de'i rjes
NK041(di)035:791: nga ni 'di nas mi snang nas //
NK041(di)035:792: lo ni brgyad dang bcu gnyis na //
NK041(di)035:793: lha gnas gsum du grags pa yi //
NK041(di)035:794: bstan pa'i snying po dam pa zhig /
NK041(di)035:795: 'dzam gling shar gyi phyogs mtshams kyi //
NK041(di)035:796: rgyal po dzahzhesa bya ba la //
NK041(di)035:797: bsod nams chen po'i mthus snang ba'i //
NK041(di)035:798: gsang ba'i bdag pos snang bar 'gyur //
NK041(di)035:799: zhes lung bstan pa ltar rgyal po nyid kyi pho
NK041(di)035:800: brang gi khang thog tu tan+t+ra chen po sde bco
NK041(di)035:801: brgyad kyi glegs bam char du babs shing /
NK041(di)035:802: rgyal po dzahns ku ku r+aa dzah in+d+ra b+h+au ti /
NK041(di)035:803: sim ha r+aa dzah u pa r+aa dzah sras mo go ma de b+ai rnams las brgyud de /
NK041(di)035:804: thams cad tshogs kyi spyod pa'i nye rgyu la brten
NK041(di)035:805: nas rang rang gi tshom bu dang bcas pa rdo
NK041(di)035:806: rje 'chang chen po'i sa la mngon du gshegs pa
NK041(di)035:807: sha stag go // sras mos sgeg pa rdo rje dang slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang ba /
NK041(di)035:808: de gnyis kas pan chen bi ma la mi tra /
NK041(di)035:809: des bod du lo ts+aa ba rma gnyags gnyis /
NK041(di)035:810: rma rin chen mchog nas mkhas pa gtsug gyer rnam gnyis las zhang dang /
NK041(di)035:811: gnyags lo ye shes gzhon nus sog po dpal ye la brgyud de /
NK041(di)035:812: zhang dang sog pos gnubs chen sangs rgyas ye shes la bskur /
NK041(di)035:813: de nas gnubs yon tan rgya mtsho yab sras dang /
NK041(di)035:814: chos lung gi nyang khu dbon nas lha rje zur po che sh+aakya 'byung gnas /
NK041(di)035:815: de'i slob ma rtse mo bzhi las lta sgom gyi rtse mor zung chung shes rabs grags /
NK041(di)035:816: de'i slob ma ka bzhi dang glan sh+aaka byang las
NK041(di)035:817: gsang bdag chen po sgro phug pa sh+aakya seng ge
NK041(di)035:819: kho bo cag gi bla ma dam pa bka' drin
NK041(di)035:820: mnyam med 'di zhes bya bas bdag rgyud dbang gi
NK041(di)035:821: chu bos smin par mdzad pa yin /
NK041(di)035:822: brgyud pa de las byung ba'i chos de la'ang lam gyi gzhi smin byed dbang gi rim pa dang /
NK041(di)035:823: de'i nyams len grol byed bskyed rdzogs kyi rim pa
NK041(di)035:824: gnyis su yod pas 'dir dbang bskur ba'i rim pa
NK041(di)035:825: de skabs su bab pa yin /
NK041(di)035:826: de nas sta gon gyi tshe /
NK041(di)035:829: rdo rje 'chang gis gsungs pa ste //
NK041(di)035:830: zhes dbang bskur ba yang dkyil 'khor sngon du 'gro ba can yin pas //
NK041(di)035:834: gzugs brnyan lhag pa'i gzugs brnyan gsum //
NK041(di)035:835: byang chub sems dang tshogs mchog bstan //
NK041(di)035:836: zhes bdun du gsungs kyang gang du dbang bskur ba'i
NK041(di)035:837: dkyil 'khor ni gang zag gi rgyud tshod dang sbyar
NK041(di)035:838: nas / rang bzhin ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK041(di)035:839: lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi gzugs brnyan nam sprul pa'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK041(di)035:840: rig pa nyams kyi dkyil 'khor gsum bshad pa ni 'phags pa rnams kyi spyod yul yin /
NK041(di)035:841: ting nge 'dzin la brtan pa rjes mthun tsam thob pa la sogs pa'i slob dpon gyis ni /
NK041(di)035:842: gdul bya'i dbye bas skal dman 'jug pa rdul tshon /
NK041(di)035:845: yang rab bla ma'i lus dkyil la brten pa'i tshul bzhi las /
NK041(di)035:846: 'dir da ltar gyi bla ma dam pa rnams kyi
NK041(di)035:847: phyag bzhes su rdul tshon dang ras bris gang rung
NK041(di)035:848: la brten nas dbang bskur bar mdzad pa'i tshul gnyis
NK041(di)035:853: nub dang po sta gon gyi cho ga ste /
NK041(di)035:854: de yang lha bum sta gon grub nas /
NK041(di)035:855: da slob ma sta gon gyi bya ba bsgrub pa skabs su bab pa yin pas /
NK041(di)035:856: bla ma dang dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo tha mi
NK041(di)035:857: dad pa la lhag gnas kyi chos rnams zhu ba'i
NK041(di)035:861: 'dir dbang bskur ba'i rim pa skabs su bab pa yin /
NK041(di)035:863: de la dbang gi ngo bo ni /
NK041(di)035:864: rgyu gnyis rkyen bzhi tshogs pa la brten nas go 'phang gi chos rgyud la 'jog pa'i las kyis /
NK041(di)035:865: rgyud kyi dri ma byang ba'am nyams smad par byas shing thar ba'i myu gu myur du skyes pa'am /
NK041(di)035:866: skye nges kyi sa bon khyad par can gsos thebs
NK041(di)035:867: pas lam bsgom rung dang 'bras bu thob rung gi
NK041(di)035:868: nus pa mthu can du smin par byas pa ste
NK041(di)035:869: / sa bon gsos thebs pa'i cha de sngags kyi sdom pa'ang yin la /
NK041(di)035:871: nges tshig ni a b+hi shiny+tsa'i sgra las drangs na /
NK041(di)035:872: mngon par gtor bas na dbang ste /
NK041(di)035:873: sbyang bya sgo gsum gyi dri ma gtor zhing 'khrud par byed pa'i phyir /
NK041(di)035:874: yang mngon par blugs pas na dbang ste /
NK041(di)035:875: lam bsgom rung dang 'bras bu thob rung gi nus pa khyad par can rgyud la 'jog pa'i phyir /
NK041(di)035:876: de ltar yang brtag gnyis las /
NK041(di)035:877: gtor dang blugs pa zhes bya ba //
NK041(di)035:878: des na dbang zhes brjod par bya //
NK041(di)035:880: dbye na dad pa can rjes su 'dzin pa la phan pa'i dbang bcu /
NK041(di)035:881: brtson 'grus can rjes su 'dzin pa la nus pa'i dbang lnga /
NK041(di)035:882: brtul zhugs can rjes su 'dzin pa la zab mo'i dbang gsum gsungs te /
NK041(di)035:884: dad dang brtson 'grus brtul zhugs la //
NK041(di)035:885: phan dang nus pa'i dbang bskur bya //
NK041(di)035:886: shes rab dbang bskur rim pa bcas /
NK041(di)035:887: brtse bas chud mi za bar sbyin //
NK041(di)035:889: de yang dbang bskur ba ni dkyil 'khor sngon du 'gro ba can yin la /
NK041(di)035:890: de la'ang rdo rje rtse mo las /
NK041(di)035:891: sems can shin tu gdul dka' gang //
NK041(di)035:892: sdom par 'dzin pa mi mdzad cing //
NK041(di)035:893: dad dang ldan pa med pa yang //
NK041(di)035:894: 'jug pa nyid ni dgag mi byed //
NK041(di)035:895: zhes pas re zhig dbang gi snod du ma gyur pa'i gang zag yin na'ang /
NK041(di)035:896: dkyil 'khor du bcug pa tsam la 'gal ba med par gsungs mod /
NK041(di)035:897: dkyil 'khor du ma bcug pa la dbang bskur ba ni nam du'ang mi rung zhing /
NK041(di)035:899: dkyil 'khor ma mthong ba rnams kyi mdun du ma smra zhig ces gsungs pa'i phyir /
NK041(di)035:901: kun byas dbang phyug rig pas 'jug /
NK041(di)035:902: de nas slob ma gzhug par bya //
NK041(di)035:903: zhes gsungs pa ltar sta gon du gnas pa yan chad song nas dngos gzhi la /
NK041(di)035:904: rdo rje slob dpon gyi bya ba dang /
NK041(di)035:905: rdo rje slob ma'i bya ba gnyis las /
NK041(di)035:906: slob dpon gyis bgyi 'os dkyil 'khor bzhengs pa /
NK041(di)035:908: bdag nyid dkyil 'khor du rig pas 'jug pa rnams chad lhag med par sngon du grub /
NK041(di)035:909: da khyed rang rnams kyi ngo skal du gyur pa la /
NK041(di)035:910: lha dang skal pa mnyam pa'i ched du dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa'i chos dang /
NK041(di)035:911: zhugs nas dbang nod pa'i bya ba gnyis las /
NK041(di)035:912: 'dir 'jug pa'i yan lag khrus dang bgegs bsal ba
NK041(di)035:913: sngon du song nas da bla ma dang dkyil 'khor
NK041(di)035:914: gyi gtso bo tha mi dad pa la dkyil 'khor
NK041(di)035:915: du 'jug pa'i chos rnams zhu ba'i yon du man+dala
NK041(di)035:917: des mtshon nas mdo dbang lta bu la /
NK041(di)035:918: lta ba la gtso bor brten pa rdzogs pa chen po a ti ga'o //
NK041(di)035:919: zhes pa'i bar sngar ltar las /
NK041(di)035:920: de las 'dir lung a nu yo ga /
NK041(di)035:921: de la'ang lung gi ma h+aa'i rgyu ye shes rngam pa glog gi 'khor lo lta bu /
NK041(di)035:922: lung gi lung rtsa ba'i rgyud kun 'dus rig pa lta bu /
NK041(di)035:923: lung gi a ti sems lung chen po'i mdo lta bu ste /
NK041(di)035:924: a nu'i nang gses kyi bskyed rdzogs gsum dang /
NK041(di)035:925: de thams cad kyi spyi dems dgongs pa 'dus pa'i mdo rnams las /
NK041(di)035:926: 'dir rtsa bshad kyi rgyud de thams cad dang /
NK041(di)035:927: cha mthun gyi rgyud rnam par snang mdzad thig le dbang gi tan+t+ra dang /
NK041(di)035:928: dbang bskur rgyal po sogs rgyud dang /
NK041(di)035:929: bde ba gsal mdzad kyi man ngag gis ji ltar
NK041(di)035:930: bkral ba'i dgongs don gcig tu dril ba 'dus pa
NK041(di)035:931: chen po mdo'i dkyil 'khor du dbang bskur ba skabs
NK041(di)035:933: de yang dbang don bsdus pa las /
NK041(di)035:934: sems can rnams kyi don ched du //
NK041(di)035:935: dbang gi don rnams bsdu bar bya //
NK041(di)035:936: chu bo chen po bzhi rnams la //
NK041(di)035:937: sngon byung dang ni rjes su 'jug /
NK041(di)035:938: ces pas sngon byung rgyal ba'i mdzad spyod kyi sgo nas gdul bya spro ba skyed pa'i dbang dang /
NK041(di)035:939: rjes 'jug gang zag gi nyams len gyi sgo nas
NK041(di)035:940: gdul bya chud mi za bar bskur thabs gnyis las
NK041(di)035:941: / 'dir phyi ma rjes 'jug gi dbang yin /
NK041(di)035:944: rjes 'jug las dang po pa'i dbang gnyis las /
NK041(di)035:945: snga ma lam pa'i dbang ni /
NK041(di)035:946: dbang don rnam par 'byed pa las /
NK041(di)035:947: rjes 'jug lam pa'i dbang skabs na //
NK041(di)035:948: sku ni rnal 'byor rnam pa lnga //
NK041(di)035:950: tshogs sbyor gnyis gcig tu bsdus pa mos spyod kyi lam pas dang /
NK041(di)035:954: lam bzhi la gnas pa'i slob ma la /
NK041(di)035:955: rim par chu bo bzhi'i dbang bskur bas /
NK041(di)035:956: lam 'og ma gong ma la sbyor bar gsungs pa'i phyir /
NK041(di)035:957: dang po gsum lam dbang dang /
NK041(di)035:958: phyi ma gcig po 'bras dus kyi dbang du 'gyur zhing /
NK041(di)035:959: de las 'di ni smin byed gtso che ba rjes
NK041(di)035:960: 'jug las dang po'i dbang zhes grags pa de yin
NK041(di)035:961: / de la'ang sbyangs pas snod du gyur pa'i slob
NK041(di)035:962: ma la mdo yongs rdzogs kyi lugs su bskur ba
NK041(di)035:963: / dang / rang bzhin gyi snod du gyur pa'i
NK041(di)035:964: slob ma la mdo khyad par ba'i lugs su bskur
NK041(di)035:965: / dang / ba gnyis las / 'dir de gnyis gcig tu dril nas bskur ba'i lugs yin /
NK041(di)035:966: de'ang dbang gi ngo bo ni /
NK041(di)035:968: gtor dang blug pa zhes bya ba //
NK041(di)035:969: des na dbang zhes brjod par bya //
NK041(di)035:971: zhes pa'i bar sngar ltar gyi rjes su /
NK041(di)035:972: dbye na dbang don bsdus pa las /
NK041(di)035:973: rjes 'jug las kyi dang po la //
NK041(di)035:974: chu bo bzhi yi dbang bskur bas //
NK041(di)035:975: yo ga la sogs theg drug la //
NK041(di)035:976: phyi dbang rgyud kyi chu bos bya //
NK041(di)035:977: bskyed pa ma h+aa yo ga la //
NK041(di)035:978: nang dbang 'byung ba'i chu bos bya //
NK041(di)035:979: rdzogs pa a nu yo ga la //
NK041(di)035:980: sgrub dbang grags pa'i chu bos bya //
NK041(di)035:981: rdzogs chen a ti yo ga la //
NK041(di)035:982: gsang dbang rdzogs pa'i chu bos bya //
NK041(di)035:984: de'ang lha mi'i theg pa nas yo ga'i bar bya
NK041(di)035:985: spyod so sor bgrangs pa'i theg pa bdun gyi dbang
NK041(di)035:986: nod pas / sa dang po 'gyur ba ma nges pa nas /
NK041(di)035:987: bdun pa dmigs pa 'bras bu skye ba'i bar gyi
NK041(di)035:988: sa bdun non pas yo ga ste rnal 'byor du
NK041(di)035:989: 'gyur la / nang dbang 'byung ba'i chu bo nod
NK041(di)035:990: pas sa brgyad pa gnas pa mi g.yo ba'i sa
NK041(di)035:992: sgrub dbang grags pa'i chu bo nod pas sa dgu
NK041(di)035:993: pa brdal ba chos nyid kyi sa non nas rjes
NK041(di)035:995: gsang dbang rdzogs pa'i chu bo nod pas sa bcu
NK041(di)035:996: pa rdzogs pa spyir chib kyi sa non nas shin
NK041(di)035:999: de la'ang thog mar spyi dbang chen po'i gleng gzhi
NK041(di)035:1000: dang 'brel bar sngon 'gro sgo 'byed phyag na rdo
NK041(di)035:1001: rje ngan song gnas 'dren gyi dkyil 'khor du dbang
NK041(di)035:1003: de la phyi dbang rgyud kyi chu bo las /
NK041(di)035:1004: thog mar lha mi'i dkyil 'khor du dbang bskur ba la //
NK041(di)035:1005: zhes sogs skabs bab gang yin brjod nas /
NK041(di)035:1006: sta gon yod med dang 'jug pa'i khyad par sogs
NK041(di)035:1007: sngar gyi rigs 'gres khog phub nas ma 'dres par
NK041(di)035:1008: 'dor len bya'o // yang a ti'i rtsa dbang lta bu la /
NK041(di)035:1009: rdzogs pa chen po a ti yo ga'o //
NK041(di)035:1010: zhes pa'i bar sngar ltar las /
NK041(di)035:1011: de ltar bskyed rdzogs rnam pa gsum las 'dir man ngag rdzogs pa chen po /
NK041(di)035:1012: de yang spros bral rang byung gi ye shes rgya
NK041(di)035:1013: chad phyogs lhung med pa theg pa kun gyi don
NK041(di)035:1014: thams cad yongs su rdzogs pas rtse mor gyur te
NK041(di)035:1016: gcig rdzogs gnyis rdzogs sems su rdzogs //
NK041(di)035:1017: gcig rdzogs sems kyi byas pa rdzogs //
NK041(di)035:1018: gnyis rdzogs phun sum tshogs pa rdzogs //
NK041(di)035:1019: kun rdzogs byang chub sems su rdzogs //
NK041(di)035:1021: des na ma h+aa dang a nu man chad thams
NK041(di)035:1022: cad rtsol sgrub blang dor byas pas re dogs dri
NK041(di)035:1023: mas rang byung gi ye shes la sgrib pa'i phyir
NK041(di)035:1024: / rdzogs chen gyi gol sar bshad de /
NK041(di)035:1025: nam mkha' dang mnyam pa'i rgyud las /
NK041(di)035:1027: thabs dang shes rab sgor zhugs nas //
NK041(di)035:1028: rang rgyud dag pa'i dkyil 'khor la //
NK041(di)035:1029: bsnyen sgrub rnam bzhis sgrub par byed //
NK041(di)035:1030: a ti yo ga'i bde chen ni //
NK041(di)035:1031: rtsol sgrub 'das pa'i byang chub sems //
NK041(di)035:1032: rtsol sgrub 'dod pas ma h+aa sgrib //
NK041(di)035:1033: rdzogs chen rtsol sgrub byed pa ni //
NK041(di)035:1034: ma h+aa yo ga gol bar bshad //
NK041(di)035:1035: a nu dbyer med pa 'dod pa //
NK041(di)035:1036: dbyings dang ye shes sgor zhugs nas //
NK041(di)035:1037: 'di ltar snang ba'i chos rnams la //
NK041(di)035:1038: rgyu ni dag pa'i dbyings lta ba //
NK041(di)035:1040: a ti yo ga'i bde chen ni //
NK041(di)035:1043: rdzogs chen rgyu 'bras gnyis lta na //
NK041(di)035:1044: a nu yo ga gol bar bshad //
NK041(di)035:1046: rgyu mtshan de'i phyir a ti yo ga ni bya
NK041(di)035:1047: rtsol dang bral ba'i ye shes la dbang bsgyur ba
NK041(di)035:1050: rdzogs pa chen po'i lta spyod ni //
NK041(di)035:1052: lta spyod byang chub sems 'di ni //
NK041(di)035:1053: nam mkha' lta bu'i rang bzhin te //
NK041(di)035:1054: nam mkha' la ni rtog dpyod 'das //
NK041(di)035:1055: zhes sogs rgya cher gsungs shing /
NK041(di)035:1057: rang byung ye shes rtsol med las //
NK041(di)035:1058: grol nas grol ba'i lam yang ston //
NK041(di)035:1060: rdzogs pa chen po de la'ang dbye na /
NK041(di)035:1061: a ti bkod pa chen po las /
NK041(di)035:1062: yid can rnams la sems kyi sde //
NK041(di)035:1063: nam mkha' can la klong gi sde //
NK041(di)035:1064: rim rtsol bral la man ngag sde //
NK041(di)035:1067: man ngag sde dang gsum las /
NK041(di)035:1069: phyii 'gyur bcu gsum ste ma bu bco brgyad kyi rgyud kyi dgongs pa /
NK041(di)035:1070: lo ts+aa ba chen po bee ro tsa na'i thugs kyi nying khu /
NK041(di)035:1071: sems sde nyang lugs a don bco brgyad kyi rtsal dbang bskur ba skabs su bab pa yin /
NK041(di)035:1072: de la 'dir shin tu rnal 'byor gyi lugs kyis /
NK041(di)035:1073: skal ldan 'bad med du grol bar byed pa la /
NK041(di)035:1074: zhes sogs dbang chog gi dkyus bzhin shes par bya'o //
NK041(di)035:1075: yang na raka dong sprugs la /
NK041(di)035:1076: rdzogs pa chen po a ti yo ga'o //
NK041(di)035:1077: zhes pa'i bar sngar ltar la /
NK041(di)035:1078: de las 'dir bskyed rdzogs rnam gsum gyi sgor zhugs
NK041(di)035:1079: pa'i rnal 'byor pa rnams kyi nyams chag bskang zhing
NK041(di)035:1081: sems can thams cad ngan song gi sdug bsngal las
NK041(di)035:1082: drangs nas bla na med pa'i dngos grub kyi skal
NK041(di)035:1083: pa can du byed pa'i thabs mkhas kyi sgo rmad
NK041(di)035:1084: du byung ba / rnal 'byor spyi khrus na raka
NK041(di)035:1085: dong sprugs mtshams med lnga sbyong gi dkyil 'khor du
NK041(di)035:1086: dbang bskur ba skabs su bab pa yin /
NK041(di)035:1087: de la'ang rgyud dang man ngag so so'i dgongs pas /
NK041(di)035:1088: glang po che rab 'bogs kyi rtog pa gcig khol
NK041(di)035:1089: du phyung ba kalpa dum bu'i rgyud dri ma med
NK041(di)035:1090: pa bshags pa'i rgyud kyi le'u gsum pa slob dpon
NK041(di)035:1091: chen po pad+ma'i gdams ngag gis bkral ba zhi khro
NK041(di)035:1092: khrom dkrugs su grags pa dang /
NK041(di)035:1093: pad+mas mdzad pa'i sgrub thabs rgya zhang khrom gyi gter
NK041(di)035:1094: ma'i rjes su 'brangs pas bshags rgyud kyi le'u'i go
NK041(di)035:1095: rim ltar zhi khro gnas bsgyur dang /
NK041(di)035:1096: yi ge brgya pa phrin las kyi rgyud sogs la brten pa'i zhi khro rigs bsdus dang /
NK041(di)035:1097: zhi khro rang gzhung la dong sprug gis kha bskangs
NK041(di)035:1098: ba zhi khro rab 'byams su grags pa rnams las
NK041(di)035:1099: / 'dir zhi khro rigs bsdus pad+ma brgya ldan gyi dkyil 'khor ram /
NK041(di)035:1100: zhi khro khrom dkrug gi dkyil 'khor du dbang bskur bar byed pa yin /
NK041(di)035:1101: de yang 'gyod tshangs kyi rgyal po 'di ji ltar byung ba'i khungs kyi gleng gzhi ni /
NK041(di)035:1102: sngon 'dod khams kyi gnas 'di na bram ze dung
NK041(di)035:1103: gi phreng ba can zhes bya ba rig pa'i gnas
NK041(di)035:1104: lnga la mkhas pa zhig la /
NK041(di)035:1105: slob ma rgyal po'i bu zhig yod pas des slob sbyong mthar phyin pa na /
NK041(di)035:1106: da ni nga yi gong na rig par smra ba slob dpon 'di tsam du zad pas /
NK041(di)035:1107: 'di gong du mi btang ngo snyam du bsam nas slob dpon la tho 'tshams shing /
NK041(di)035:1108: slob dpon gyis kyang zhe sdang gis dmod bor ba'i
NK041(di)035:1109: las kyis gnyis ka ngan 'gror ltung nas sdug bsngal
NK041(di)035:1110: gyis nyam thag par gyur pa las yul dang 'phrad
NK041(di)035:1112: dpal rdo rje sems dpa' mngon du byon nas 'gyod
NK041(di)035:1113: tshangs kyi bshags pa dang yig brgya'i gsang sngags bstan
NK041(di)035:1114: pas sngon gyi gnas dran te 'gyod pa drag po
NK041(di)035:1115: skyes pa la / gsang ba'i bdag pos phyi nang
NK041(di)035:1116: gsang ba'i dbang bskur bas dge ba'i gsos thebs te
NK041(di)035:1117: skyes pa la / / byang chub kyi myu gu
NK041(di)035:1118: skyes pa'i rim gyis rig 'dzin gyi sa la gnas
NK041(di)035:1119: skyes pa la / / par gyur to // nyams
NK041(di)035:1120: chags sbyong ba'i thabs phul du byung ba de nyid
NK041(di)035:1121: phyis mi yi yul du ji ltar dar ba ni
NK041(di)035:1122: skyes pa la / / par gyur to // /
NK041(di)035:1123: gsang bdag gi mthus rgyal po dzahl tan+t+ra sde bco
NK041(di)035:1124: brgyad kyi glegs bam char du bab pa'i nang tshan
NK041(di)035:1125: skyes pa la / / par gyur to // /
NK041(di)035:1126: / glang po che rab 'bogs kyi le'u gsum pa
NK041(di)035:1127: khol du phyung ba dum bu'i rgyud la sogs pa
NK041(di)035:1128: rgyal po dzahns tshom bu'i rig 'dzin rnams la brgyud
NK041(di)035:1129: skyes pa la / / par gyur to // /
NK041(di)035:1130: / de / sangs rgyas gsang ba'i man ngag bi
NK041(di)035:1131: skyes pa la / / par gyur to // /
NK041(di)035:1132: / de / ma la / slob dpon chen po
NK041(di)035:1133: pad+ma nas gnyags lo ye shes gzhon nu la bka'
NK041(di)035:1134: skyes pa la / / par gyur to // /
NK041(di)035:1135: / de / ma la / babs shing / de
NK041(di)035:1137: gnubs chen sangs rgyas ye shes /
NK041(di)035:1139: zhu ston gzhon nu snying po /
NK041(di)035:1141: zur che chung nas rim par brgyud de //
NK041(di)035:1142: dpal ldan bla ma dam pa 'di zhes bya ba las /
NK041(di)035:1143: kho bos legs par thob pa ni gang las byung ba brgyud pa'i lo rgyus yin la /
NK041(di)035:1144: de las byung ba'i gdams pa de la /
NK041(di)035:1145: phyi nang gsang ba'i bshags pa'i sgo nas nyams chag skong ba'i cho ga dang /
NK041(di)035:1146: dbang bskur ba'i rim pa gnyis las /
NK041(di)035:1148: de la'ang rdo rje slob dpon gyis bgyi 'os dang /
NK041(di)035:1150: yang gter ma la mtshon na /
NK041(di)035:1151: khyad par de ldan gyi gsang sngags rnying ma de la'ang /
NK041(di)035:1155: zhes pas bar sngar ltar las /
NK041(di)035:1156: de ltar brgyud pa'i bka' srol gsum du gnas pa las /
NK041(di)035:1161: khyad par gyi brgyud pa gsum dang /
NK041(di)035:1162: gtso bor brgyud thag nye bas byin rlabs kyi tshan kha che zhing /
NK041(di)035:1163: gter yig gi dpe dpang mnga' bas khungs btsun pa dang /
NK041(di)035:1164: gang la gang 'dul gyi dus dang mtshams par mngon
NK041(di)035:1165: par snang bas zab lam nub pa med pa'i phyir
NK041(di)035:1166: / khyad par du 'phags pa gter gyi phyogs su gtogs pa yin /
NK041(di)035:1167: deng sang bka' ma rnams dus dbang gis rim par nub cing 'chal ba'i tshe /
NK041(di)035:1168: las 'phro sad pa'i skal ldan rnams gter chos kyis
NK041(di)035:1169: rang dang gzhan gyi don rlabs po che dka' ba
NK041(di)035:1170: med par 'grub par 'gyur ba la dgongs nas /
NK041(di)035:1171: rgyud lung man ngag gi bcud thams cad gangs ri'i
NK041(di)035:1172: phreng bas bskor ba'i ljongs bod yul gyi ri brag
NK041(di)035:1173: mtsho gsum gtsug lag khang sogs su mi 'jig pa'i
NK041(di)035:1174: phyag rgyas btab ste sba bar mdzad pa'i dgos pa
NK041(di)035:1176: shin tu zab pa'i mthar thug snying po rnams //
NK041(di)035:1177: spyir yang bod rnams gsar ngas che ba dang //
NK041(di)035:1178: snyigs ma'i 'gro la lhag par snying rje bas //
NK041(di)035:1179: mtha' dbus thams cad gter gyis bkang nas bzhag /
NK041(di)035:1180: las can bu dang 'phrad pa'i smon lam btab //
NK041(di)035:1181: ma 'ongs dus su rtog ge tha snyad can //
NK041(di)035:1182: sgom chen la sogs phyogs dang ris dregs can //
NK041(di)035:1183: rang che 'byin cing gter la rtsod na yang //
NK041(di)035:1184: snyigs ma'i chos byed phal cher gter gyis 'dren //
NK041(di)035:1185: zab la kha tshang ma bsgribs mtha' rgyas shing //
NK041(di)035:1186: gdams pa sna res gang zag grol bar nges //
NK041(di)035:1187: de bas las sad skal ldan sbyangs pa can //
NK041(di)035:1188: 'chi ba dran na gter chos nyams su longs //
NK041(di)035:1189: tshe gcig thar lam thob po rjes 'jug rnams //
NK041(di)035:1191: bod dang bod chen po'i yul 'dir rgyu ba'i skye
NK041(di)035:1192: dgu rnams kyi phan bde'i rtsa lag dus bab kyi
NK041(di)035:1193: zab gter la rag las pa yin la /
NK041(di)035:1194: de nyid spyan 'dren pa po yang /
NK041(di)035:1195: sngon gyi lo pan dang rgyal blon sa chen po la bzhugs pa'i 'phags chen rnams /
NK041(di)035:1196: gang 'dul gyi sprul pa'i snang brnyan gter ston du bstan nas 'byon pa /
NK041(di)035:1198: sangs rgyas bla ma nas bde chen gling pa'i bar
NK041(di)035:1199: so so'i dus rtags dang bcas lung bstan pa las
NK041(di)035:1200: / nyang gter bka' brgyad lta bu la mtshon na /
NK041(di)035:1202: srin mo sbar rjes sbas pa'i gter kha 'di //
NK041(di)035:1203: mi bzhag 'don pa'i rtags de ston nas 'byung //
NK041(di)035:1204: mnga' bdag sprul pa nyang ral zhes bya 'byung //
NK041(di)035:1206: 'gran zla dang bral ba'i gter ston gyi rgyal po
NK041(di)035:1207: mnga' bdag nyang nyi ma 'od zer gyi spyan 'dren
NK041(di)035:1208: par mdzad pa'i chos gter mtha' yas pa zhig bzhugs
NK041(di)035:1209: pa las / 'dir sgrub chen bde gshegs 'dus pa /
NK041(di)035:1210: de la snga 'gyur rnams rgyud sde dang sgrub sde
NK041(di)035:1211: zhes bka' yi babs so gnyis su 'byed pa las
NK041(di)035:1212: / 'di ni sgrub sde brgyad gcig tu dril nas sgrub pa rtsa ba lta bur gyur pa yin /
NK041(di)035:1213: de yang spyir de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi
NK041(di)035:1214: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga'i bdag nyid
NK041(di)035:1216: de sgrub pa'i thabs kyi sgo yang rnam pa lngar 'gyur te /
NK041(di)035:1217: 'jam dpal gyi sku 'khor lo bzhi la brten nas bde gshegs sku'i sgrub pa dang /
NK041(di)035:1218: rta skad thengs gsum la brten nas pad+ma gsung gi sgrub pa dang /
NK041(di)035:1219: thugs rig pa rang byung gi ye shes yang dag
NK041(di)035:1220: grub pa gcig pu la brten nas thugs rdo rje'i
NK041(di)035:1221: sgrub pa dang / 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad
NK041(di)035:1222: yon tan du rdzogs par ston pa bdud rtsi yon
NK041(di)035:1224: mngon spyod kyi phrin las kyis gdug pa tshar gcod
NK041(di)035:1225: pa'i thabs gtso bor ston pa phur pa phrin las
NK041(di)035:1226: kyi sgrub pa ste ye shes lha'i sgrub sde lnga
NK041(di)035:1227: dang / 'das ma 'das kyi sgrub sde thun mong ba ma mo rbod gtong dang /
NK041(di)035:1229: 'jig rten mchod bstod kyi sgrub sde ste /
NK041(di)035:1230: de gsum yang ye shes lha'i sgrub pa rnams kyi bstan pa srung ba la dgongs nas /
NK041(di)035:1231: las ka bsam gyis mi khyab pa zhig gsungs pa yin cing /
NK041(di)035:1232: de thams cad gcig tu dril nas sgrub pa'i thabs /
NK041(di)035:1233: 'dir sgrub chen bde gshegs 'dus pa'i dkyil 'khor du dbang bskur bar byed pa las /
NK041(di)035:1234: thog mar nges shes 'dren pa lo rgyus kyi dbang du byas na /
NK041(di)035:1235: ston pa bcom ldan 'das dpal kun tu bzang po
NK041(di)035:1236: nyid chos sku skye ba med pa las ma g.yos
NK041(di)035:1237: bzhin du gzugs sku'i rol pa zhi ba dang khro
NK041(di)035:1238: bo dpal he ru ka'i rnam par bzhengs nas /
NK041(di)035:1239: 'og min gsang ba mchog gi gnas su /
NK041(di)035:1240: 'khor sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' khro bo
NK041(di)035:1241: dang khro mo sogs bsam gyis mi khyab pa la
NK041(di)035:1242: / chos nyid kyi rang sgras spyi rgyud lnga /
NK041(di)035:1243: sgos rgyud bcu la sogs te sgrub sde'i rgyud mtha' yas pa gsungs /
NK041(di)035:1244: de rnams rig 'dzin gyi gtso bo gsang bdag rdo rje chos kyis thog mar ngag tu bsdus /
NK041(di)035:1245: de nas pusti glegs bam la bkod cing /
NK041(di)035:1246: dgongs 'grel du lung lnga yang mdzad de /
NK041(di)035:1247: mkha' 'gro las kyi dbang mo che la gtad /
NK041(di)035:1248: des spyi dang bye brag gi rgyud so sor phyes
NK041(di)035:1249: nas rin po che'i sgrom bur bcugs te bsil ba
NK041(di)035:1250: tshal gyi mchod rten bde byed brtsegs par gter du
NK041(di)035:1251: sbas / nam zhig na slob dpon brgyad kyi gzigs
NK041(di)035:1252: snang mthun par cho 'phrul sna tshogs snang bas gnas
NK041(di)035:1253: der byon nas sde brgyad rnams la bka' bsgos pas
NK041(di)035:1254: sbas / / gter srung rnams kyis bye brag gi
NK041(di)035:1255: rgyud kyi sgrom bu brgyad po bka' babs kyi rig
NK041(di)035:1257: spyi rgyud kyi sgrom rin po che sna brgyad las
NK041(di)035:1258: byas pa slar gter du sbas pa slob dpon chen
NK041(di)035:1259: po pad+ma 'byung gnas kyis spyan drangs /
NK041(di)035:1260: de la slob dpon chen po 'di ni dus gsum
NK041(di)035:1261: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi gsung rdo rje'i bdag nyid
NK041(di)035:1262: 'od dpag tu med pa'i ngo bo las ma g.yos
NK041(di)035:1263: bzhin du thugs rje'i rang rtsal ma 'gag pa'i cho
NK041(di)035:1264: 'phrul 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug dang /
NK041(di)035:1265: dbang chen rta mgrin sogs gang la gang 'dul gyi
NK041(di)035:1266: rnam par rol pa mtha' yas pa ston pa las
NK041(di)035:1267: / khyad par 'dzam bu gling du thub pa'i dbang
NK041(di)035:1268: po'i rgyal tshabs su d+ha na ko sha'i mtsho gling
NK041(di)035:1269: du pad sdong las sku bltams pa'i tshul bstan te
NK041(di)035:1270: / / rgya bod kun tu sangs rgyas kyi bstan
NK041(di)035:1271: pa la ston pa gnyis pa lta bur gyur cing
NK041(di)035:1272: / / / khyad par bsam yas mchims phu brag
NK041(di)035:1273: dmar ke'u tshang du rje 'bangs nyi shu rtsa lnga
NK041(di)035:1274: la sgrub chen bka' brgyad kyi dkyil 'khor zhal phyes
NK041(di)035:1276: bka' babs kyi grub chen brgyad kyi me tog tshom
NK041(di)035:1277: bu'i gtso bo so sos bzhes pa dang mthun par
NK041(di)035:1278: sgrub gnas brgyad du bsgrub tu btang zhing /
NK041(di)035:1279: rje 'bangs de thams cad kyis grub pa brnyes /
NK041(di)035:1280: de'i nang nas kyang mnga' bdag khri srong lde'u btsan la bde gshegs 'dus pa'i bka' babs pas /
NK041(di)035:1281: rgyud lung man ngag thams cad lo chen bee ro
NK041(di)035:1282: tsa na dang ldan ma rtse mang gis lo ts+aa
NK041(di)035:1283: byas te bsgyur bshad kyis gtan la phab nas gsungs
NK041(di)035:1284: / rgyal po nyid rang skal bar ldan kyang srid kyis yengs nas thugs nyams su ma lon pas /
NK041(di)035:1285: gu ru'i gsungs bzhin skye srid phyi ma la 'phrad pa'i smon lam btab ste /
NK041(di)035:1286: bla dpe rnams brag dmar mgrin bzang du gter du sbas /
NK041(di)035:1287: de nyid mkha' 'gro rnams kyis phyis mkho mthing rnam snang gi rgyab tu gter sgo spos /
NK041(di)035:1288: slad kyis bsam yas dbu rtse'i khor sa bar ma
NK041(di)035:1289: nas kha byang grub thob dngos grub kyis bton te
NK041(di)035:1290: phul ba ltar / mnga' bdag nyang nyi ma 'od
NK041(di)035:1291: zer gyis mkho mthing nas bde gshegs 'dus pa'i skor
NK041(di)035:1293: bka' bab kyi bu lnga dang /
NK041(di)035:1294: khyad par sras chung 'gro ba'i mgon po sogs skal
NK041(di)035:1295: ldan gyi slob ma rnams smin grol la 'god par
NK041(di)035:1296: mdzad / de las brgyud pa'i khyad par du ma
NK041(di)035:1297: zhig pan chen pad+ma dbang rgyal la babs pa nas
NK041(di)035:1299: bla ma dam pa 'di zhes bya ba'i drung du kho bos legs par thob pa yin /
NK041(di)035:1300: brgyud pa de las byung ba'i chos de la'ang /
NK041(di)035:1301: lam gyi gzhi smin byed dbang gi rim pa dang /
NK041(di)035:1302: de dang rjes su 'brel ba'i grol byed bskyed rdzogs kyi rim pa gnyis su yod pa las /
NK041(di)035:1303: 'dir dbang bskur ba'i rim pa de sgrub pa skabs su bab pa yin /
NK041(di)035:1304: de nas sta gon gyi tshe /
NK041(di)035:1306: zhes sogs sgyu 'phrul zhi khro sor bzhag dang /
NK041(di)035:1309: nges tshig gi bshad pa sgyu 'phrul ltar blang rjes /
NK041(di)035:1311: phyi dbang rdzas la brten nas bskur ba dang /
NK041(di)035:1312: nang dbang lus la brten te bskur ba dang /
NK041(di)035:1313: gsang dbang yum la brten te bskur ba dang /
NK041(di)035:1314: de kho na nyid sems la brten te bskur ba dang bzhi yod cing /
NK041(di)035:1315: de yang dbang bskur ba ni /
NK041(di)035:1316: dkyil 'khor sngon du 'gro ba can yin pas /
NK041(di)035:1317: thog mar dkyil 'khor du 'jug dgos te /
NK041(di)035:1320: slob dpon dang ni slob ma'o //
NK041(di)035:1321: zhes rdo rje slob dpon gyi bgyis 'os dkyil 'khor
NK041(di)035:1322: bzhengs sgrub bdag nyid 'jug pa dang bcas pa song
NK041(di)035:1323: nas / da khyed rang rnams kyi ngo skal du gyur pa la /
NK041(di)035:1328: tha ma pad gling ste gsang rdzogs lugs gsum dang /
NK041(di)035:1329: byang gter rang byung rang shar sogs bka' brgyad spyi
NK041(di)035:1330: bka' rnams so so'i sgos chos bsgyur kha ma gtogs
NK041(di)035:1331: khog 'dra zhing / sgos bka' yang dag /
NK041(di)035:1334: phur pa sogs la sgrub sde'i spyi babs kyi bshad pa 'dra ba la /
NK041(di)035:1335: de'i nang nas 'di dang 'di zhes ngos bzung zhing /
NK041(di)035:1336: de yang bka' gter dag snang gi sde gar gtogs dmigs phyed pa dang /
NK041(di)035:1337: der ma zad gter ma bla rdzogs thugs gsum sogs gzhan dang gzhan la rigs 'gres shes dgos te /
NK041(di)035:1338: gter ma rgya ches pas thams cad brjod yang mi nus shing /
NK041(di)035:1339: bshad pa'i 'khyog mtshams kyi bsgyur kha yang ha cang
NK041(di)035:1340: mang na mgo 'khor ba'i gnas su 'gro nyan snang
NK041(di)035:1341: bas re zhig de tsam mo //
NK041(di)035:1342: zhes blo dman rnams la phan pa'i phyir tshul 'di
NK041(di)035:1343: lta bu zhig brtsam dgos zhes thangs la mkhar sprul
NK041(di)035:1344: sku rin po che ngag dbang kun bzang rang grol
NK041(di)035:1345: gyis gsung gis bskul bar mdzad pa'i bka' ma chog
NK041(di)035:1346: par gnyos btsun rmongs pa d+harma sh+r+ais zin bris sug
